::DarkMouse::
She was glad for the help. And it was boring working by herself.
She climbed up to the lazar controls and stood next to Quickstrike.
"This button here activated the lazar.  Use the joystick to control the 
angel of the lazar.  This blue button will make tha lazar more consitrated 
and give you a finer and more pinpoint beam.  This orange buttom will widen 
the beam for excavating the larger portions of the tunnel."
She was about to climb down when she turned and faced Quickstrike.
"Uhmm, Thanks for the help commander."
She climbed down and stood just off to the side of the lazar.
"Aim the beam for right there commander."
She pointed to the center of the back wall.

Quickstrike:


Quickstrike nodded to Dark Mouse. "Sure thing." Sugar-bot almost slipped, 
but he caught himself before it went past his voice. She wasn't sugar-bot  
yet.

He looked at the drill, studing it. He moved closer to it. "So, what do ah 
supos'd t' do?" Maybe it wasn't the best idea that he operate this machine, 
since he wasn't the best when it came to heavy machinery. He honestly didn't 
have the hands for it. But he wanted to do something.
